'''麗莎·爾文失蹤案'''，發生於2011年10月4日清晨，10个月21天大的女婴麗莎·芮內·爾文（Lisa Renée Irwin）在[[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]][[堪薩斯城_(密蘇里州)|堪薩斯市]]的家裡被通報失蹤。<ref name="cbsreport">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504083_162-20116847-504083.html|title=Search intensifies for missing Mo. baby Lisa Irwin|work=CBS News|accessdate=October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007225106/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504083_162-20116847-504083.html|archivedate=2011-10-07}}</ref><ref name="nbcreport">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nbcactionnews.com/dpp/news/local_news/amber-alert-issued-for-missing-10-month-old-girl-in-kcmo#ixzz1ZogwHwzt|title=Second day of search for Lisa Irwin begins|accessdate=October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005030050/http://www.nbcactionnews.com/dpp/news/local_news/amber-alert-issued-for-missing-10-month-old-girl-in-kcmo#ixzz1ZogwHwzt|archivedate=2011-10-05}}</ref><ref name="huffreport">{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/10/09/lisa-irwin-missing-statistics-stranger_n_1002196.html|title=Lisa Irwin Missing: Missouri Baby Unlikely Taken By Stranger|last=Hoffer|first=Steven|work=Huffington Post|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118163055/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/10/09/lisa-irwin-missing-statistics-stranger_n_1002196.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事發經過 ==

麗莎的母親黛博菈·布萊德利（Deborah Bradley）供稱，麗莎的父親傑瑞米·爾文（Jeremy Irwin），約在10月4日（週二）的上午4點發現她失蹤了。黛博菈說在（週一）下午6點40分，她去照顧麗莎時還在床上。但當傑瑞米結束深夜工作返家時，他發現「房子裡很多盞燈都亮著，一扇窗戶開著，前門也沒鎖」。<ref name="huffreport"/>稍晚，這家人告訴警方家裡很多支手機也不見了。<ref name="huffreport"/>

後續調查中，有兩位目擊證人表示，曾看到一個男子抱著嬰兒走在路上。<ref name="abc-dog">{{Cite web|url=http://www.kmbc.com/Lisa-Irwin-Search-Warrant-Reveals-Cadaver-Dog-Hit/-/11664900/12264286/-/108618q/-/index.html|title=Lisa Irwin Search Warrant Reveals Cadaver Dog Hit|accessdate=October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130628031255/http://www.kmbc.com/Lisa-Irwin-Search-Warrant-Reveals-Cadaver-Dog-Hit/-/11664900/12264286/-/108618q/-/index.html|archivedate=2013-06-28}}</ref>警方後來找到一個符合其中一名證人描述的男子，但另一名證人則表示根據照片，該男不是他們看到的那個人。<ref name="abcvideo-manbaby">{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/baby-lisa-police-interview-key-witness-14808369|title=Baby Lisa: Police Re-Interview Key Witness | Video - ABC News|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118101103/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/baby-lisa-police-interview-key-witness-14808369|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="abc-surveillance">{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/baby-lisa-irwin-surveillance-footage-mystery-man/story?id=14795844|title=Baby Lisa Irwin: New Surveillance Footage of Mystery Man|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118163554/http://abcnews.go.com/US/baby-lisa-irwin-surveillance-footage-mystery-man/story?id=14795844|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年10月19日，警方對爾文家展開搜索，法院文件顯示警犬在靠近母親的床鋪附近時，有嗅聞到屍體氣味的反應 。<ref name="abc-dog" />執行搜索從爾文家帶走的東西包括：一條彩色被子、紫色短褲、一件彩色迪士尼角色圖案的上衣、一個毛毛蟲玩具、一條汽車總動員的卡通圖案毛毯、幾捲膠帶和一個膠帶台。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hlntv.com/article/2011/10/24/baby-lisas-parents-attend-vigil-0|title=Baby Lisa’s Parents Attend Vigil|last=Loiaconi|first=Stephen|date=2012-03-14|publisher=HLNtv.com|accessdate=2013-06-09|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016112701/http://www.hlntv.com/article/2011/10/24/baby-lisas-parents-attend-vigil-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

黛博菈在接受[[美联社|美聯社]]訪問時表示，警方指控她是涉案人，還宣稱在她測謊沒有通過時，警方告訴她：「妳做的。就是妳做的。」<ref name="cbs-followup">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/10/08/national/main20117737.shtml|title=Statistics: Mo. baby unlikely taken by stranger|work=CBS News|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515103029/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/10/08/national/main20117737.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cbs-bradlyaccused">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/10/07/national/main20117221.shtml|title=Missing baby's mom: Cops said I did it|work=CBS News|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104020613/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/10/07/national/main20117221.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>黛博菈和傑瑞米一週後宣布他們在籌措懸賞獎金，希望能獲得更多新資訊。

傑瑞米·爾文在《[[今天_(NBC)|今日秀]]》受訪時說：「我們只是想讓大家都知道我們持續與警方合作。我們還在跟警方溝通。我們竭盡所能想找到麗莎，把她帶回家。」<ref name="ibtimes">{{Cite news|url=http://newyork.ibtimes.com/articles/228288/20111010/baby-lisa-irwin-missing-police-break-in.htm|title=Baby Lisa Irwin Missing: Police Stage 'Break- In' for More Clues|accessdate=October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011085548/http://newyork.ibtimes.com/articles/228288/20111010/baby-lisa-irwin-missing-police-break-in.htm|archivedate=2011-10-11}}</ref>黛博菈當時也在場。

根據新聞報導，10月時，有一位匿名善心人士僱了一個私家偵探，還為尋獲麗莎提供十萬美金的懸賞。<ref name="anonymous-reward">{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/missing-baby-lisa-irwin-infants-brothers-submit-dna/story?id=14817602|title=Baby Lisa's Brothers: Interviews and DNA Sampling Scheduled|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118163224/http://abcnews.go.com/US/missing-baby-lisa-irwin-infants-brothers-submit-dna/story?id=14817602|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年10月，辛蒂·蕭（Cyndy Short）表示她無法再與另一位委任律師喬·塔可皮納（Joe Tacopina）共事，因此終止與爾文家的代理關係。<ref name="fox-cyndyleaves">{{Cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2011/10/31/kansas-city-attorney-leaves-case-missing-baby-lisa-irwin/|title=Kansas City Attorney Leaves Case of Missing Baby Lisa Irwin|work=Fox News|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2012-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313022628/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2011/10/31/kansas-city-attorney-leaves-case-missing-baby-lisa-irwin/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="abc-cyndyleaves">{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/missing-baby-lisa-irwin-interviews-brothers-canceled-attorney/story?id=14834151|title=Missing Baby Lisa: Interviews with Brothers Canceled, Attorney Dismissed|accessdate=October 2011|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118162915/http://abcnews.go.com/US/missing-baby-lisa-irwin-interviews-brothers-canceled-attorney/story?id=14834151|dead-url=no}}</ref>麗莎的兩個哥哥也曾因案預定將接受調查，及採集DNA樣本，但委任律師塔可皮納表示，他們的父母在前一晚取消調查<ref>{{Cite web|title=New York Criminal Defense Attorneys | Law Offices of Tacopina & Seigel|url=https://www.tacopinalaw.com/attorneys/|accessdate=2019-07-06|work=www.tacopinalaw.com|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314064654/https://www.tacopinalaw.com/attorneys/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而且據說還禁止調查員跟他們見面。<ref name="abc-cyndyleaves"/>2011年11月10日，兩個男孩第二次接受調查。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504083_162-57323065-504083/missing-kansas-city-baby-lisa-irwins-brothers-interviewed-again/|title=Missing Kansas City baby Lisa Irwin's brothers interviewed again - Crimesider|date=|publisher=CBS News|accessdate=2013-06-09|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426202203/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504083_162-57323065-504083/missing-kansas-city-baby-lisa-irwins-brothers-interviewed-again|dead-url=no}}</ref>一位申請搜索票的警探宣稱，案情關係人的各種說法，可能在調查前期就造成不良影響。<ref name="abc-surveillance"/>

2012年5月，黛博菈·布萊德利和傑瑞米·爾文向警方通報他們的簽帳卡在一個偽造出生證明的網站上被盜用。《今日秀》和《America Live》都證實這個網站確實存在。委任律師也證實他去看過這個網站。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/47502881/ns/today-today_news/t/missing-baby-lisa-debit-card-fraud-clue/#.T8qf7tVYvGE|title=Missing baby Lisa: Is debit card fraud a clue?|date=2012-05-21|publisher=Today.msnbc.msn.com|accessdate=2013-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524051233/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/47502881/ns/today-today_news/t/missing-baby-lisa-debit-card-fraud-clue#.T8qf7tVYvGE|archive-date=2012-05-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>警方表示他們持續調查，他們也相信爾文還活著。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kshb.com/dpp/news/region_missouri/northland/family-friends-release-balloons-for-baby-lisa|title=Family, friends release balloons for Baby Lisa|date=2012-06-23|publisher=Kshb.com|accessdate=2013-06-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130083628/http://www.kshb.com/dpp/news/region_missouri/northland/family-friends-release-balloons-for-baby-lisa|archivedate=2013-01-30}}</ref>

2013年10月，希臘的吉普賽營地發現一個疑似麗莎的女孩。後來官方證實這個女孩不是麗莎·爾文。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kctv5.com/story/23751427/fbi-investigates-whether-abducted-girl-found-in-greece-is-lisa-irwin|title=FBI investigates whether abducted girl found in Greece is Lisa Irwin|last=DeAnn Smith|date=November 21, 2013|publisher=KCTV5|accessdate=2014-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214155800/http://www.kctv5.com/story/23751427/fbi-investigates-whether-abducted-girl-found-in-greece-is-lisa-irwin|archive-date=2014-02-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

